title: SIP-08 Mint NFT for Community Design Winners
body:
First of all, thanks for community support. 
The winners of SakeSwap MEME/GIF competition were chosen by the community. And all selected designs will be converted to NFTs and airdropped to winners. NFT has become an exciting, highly valued movement in the blockchain space, with impressive innovation and growing traction. It is proposed to use SakeLock to support the NFT minting.
- The NFTs will be mined by SAKE, and the minting process is irreversible.
- SAKE value is transferred to NFT which means the total supply of SAKE is reduced.
- Total 35000 SAKE from SakeLock will be used to mint 26 NFTs.
- NFTs can be freely traded.

The new NFT minting feature is planned to launch. Users can mint NFT with SAKE on their own then.

 
- Yes, I support this proposal.
- No, I don’t.

---
  首先感谢SAKE社群积极参与以SakeSwap为设计主题的图片和动图有奖赛。
  最终的获奖设计作品由社群共同参与投票得出。社群成员创作的SakeSwap相关图片和动图设计将被铸造成NFT并空投给设计者。NFT是区块链里一个新热点，提议使用SakeLock支持此次NFT铸造，并正式开启新NFT板块。
  - NFT由SAKE铸造，不可解铸造
  - SAKE价值转移到NFT, SAKE总数量减少
  - 一共26枚NFT将被铸造，合计35000SAKE
  - NFT可在市场上自由交易

开始NFT板块后，计划上线用户可自行使用SAKE铸造NFT的新功能。
